MOSuite: R package for downstream multi-omics analysis

Source: R/MOSuite-package.R
MOSuite-package.Rd

Designed for differential RNA-seq analysis or any data represented in a counts table.

Details

See the website for more information, documentation, and examples: https://ccbr.github.io/MOSuite
